  "pseudonymized_text": "To: All Staff\nFrom: [FULL_NAME_1], VP of Operations\nDate: June 15, 2024\nSubject: Office Relocation and Updated Contact Information\n\nDear Team,\n\nI am writing to inform you that our company, [ORGANIZATION_NAME_1], will be relocating from our current office at [BUILDING_NUMBER_1] [STREET_1], [APARTMENT_NUMBER_1], [CITY_1], [STATE_1] [ZIP_CODE_1] to our new headquarters at [BUILDING_NUMBER_2] [STREET_2], [APARTMENT_NUMBER_2], [CITY_2], [STATE_2] [ZIP_CODE_2], effective August 1, 2024.\n\nPlease note the following important updates:\n\nEMPLOYEE CONTACTS:\n- [FULL_NAME_2] (CEO): [EMAIL_1], [PHONE_1]\n- [FULL_NAME_1] (VP Operations): [EMAIL_2], [PHONE_2]\n- [FULL_NAME_3] (IT Director): [EMAIL_3], [PHONE_3]\n\nUPDATED BANKING INFORMATION:\nOur new corporate banking details for vendor payments:\nBank: [ORGANIZATION_NAME_2]\nAccount Name: [ORGANIZATION_NAME_1]\nRouting Number: [ROUTING_NUMBER_1]\nAccount Number: [ACCOUNT_NUMBER_1]\n\nKEY DATES:\n- July 15, 2024: Packing day — all personal items must be boxed\n- August 1, 2024: First day at new location\n- August 5, 2024: Client reception at the new office\n\nCLIENT NOTIFI[STATE_2]TION:\nOur largest client, [ORGANIZATION_NAME_3], has been notified about the move. Please remind the team that the word \"apple\" in our lunch catering orders refers to the fruit, not the client — we've had confusion before. Similarly, our contact [FIRST_NAME_1] at [ORGANIZATION_NAME_3] should not be confused with the street address \"[STREET_3]\" at our current temporary storage facility at [BUILDING_NUMBER_3] [STREET_3], [CITY_3], [STATE_1] [ZIP_CODE_3].\n\nPARKING AND TRANSIT:\nFree parking is available at the Century Park garage. For questions about the LA transit system, contact [FULL_NAME_3] — that's our IT Director David, not the Century Park location.\n\nPlease send any questions to [EMAIL_4] or call our main line at [PHONE_4].\n\nBest regards,\n[FULL_NAME_1]\nEmployee ID: [EMPLOYEE_ID_1]\nSSN (for payroll verification only): [SSN_1]",
